import React from 'react'

const CrearEditarForm = (respuesta) => {
  return (
    <Form onSubmit={respuesta}>
    <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicEmail">
      <Form.Label>Titulo de la idea</Form.Label>
      <Form.Control type="text" name="idea" />
      <Form.Text className="text-muted">
        We'll never share your email with anyone else.
      </Form.Text>
    </Form.Group>

    <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicPassword">
      <Form.Label>Descripcion de la idea</Form.Label>
      <Form.Control type="text" name="descripcion" />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
      <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
    </Form.Group>
    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
      Submit
    </Button>
  </Form>  )
}

export default CrearEditarForm
